        title: "Ce este Houdini si CSS Paint API",
        content: "CSS Houdini e un set de API-uri care permite accesul la motorul de rendering CSS din JavaScript.\n\nCele mai importante API-uri:\n- Paint API (Worklet): deseneaza fundal/border custom cu Canvas 2D\n- Layout API: algoritmi de layout custom\n- Animation Worklet: animatii pe thread separat\n- Properties & Values API: proprietati CSS custom tipizate\n\nCSSPaint (Paint Worklet):\n```javascript\n// checker-painter.js\nregisterPaint('checkerboard', class {\n  static get inputProperties() { return ['--checker-size', '--checker-color']; }\n\n  paint(ctx, geom, props) {\n    const size = parseInt(props.get('--checker-size')) || 20;\n    const color = props.get('--checker-color').toString() || 'black';\n\n    for (let y = 0; y < geom.height; y += size) {\n      for (let x = 0; x < geom.width; x += size) {\n        if ((x / size + y / size) % 2 === 0) {\n          ctx.fillStyle = color;\n          ctx.fillRect(x, y, size, size);\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n});\n```\n\nFolosire:\n```javascript\nCSS.paintWorklet.addModule('checker-painter.js');\n```\n\n```css\n.element {\n  --checker-size: 30;\n  --checker-color: #6366f1;\n  background: paint(checkerboard);\n}\n```"
