        content: "Scroll-Driven Animations (CSS 2023) permit animatii trigerate de scroll fara JavaScript.\n\nanimation-timeline: scroll():\n```css\n.progress-bar {\n  width: 0%;\n  height: 4px;\n  background: #6366f1;\n  animation: grow linear;\n  animation-timeline: scroll(root inline);  /* sau block */\n  animation-duration: auto;\n}\n\n@keyframes grow {\n  from { width: 0%; }\n  to { width: 100%; }\n}\n```\n\nParametrii scroll():\n- scroller: root (document), nearest (primul parinte scrollabil), self\n- axis: block (vertical, default), inline (orizontal), x, y\n\nAnimatia progreseaza de la 0% la 100% odata cu scroll-ul de la inceput la sfarsit."
