        content: "@layer organizeaza stilurile in straturi cu prioritate controlata:\n\n```css\n/* Declara ordinea layerelor (importante): */\n@layer reset, base, components, utilities;\n\n/* Stiluri in layer: */\n@layer reset {\n  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body { margin: 0; }\n}\n\n@layer base {\n  h1 { font-size: 2rem; color: #111; }\n  a { color: #6366f1; }\n}\n\n@layer components {\n  .card { border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }\n  .btn { padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 4px; }\n}\n\n@layer utilities {\n  .text-center { text-align: center !important; }\n  .mt-4 { margin-top: 1rem !important; }\n}\n```\n\nPrioritate: stilurile unlayered > utilities > components > base > reset.\nOrdinea declararii layerelor in @layer lista stabileste prioritatea."
