        content: "Importuri cu layer:\n```css\n@import url('reset.css') layer(reset);\n@import url('bootstrap.css') layer(vendor);\n\n/* Acum Bootstrap e in layer vendor — mai slaba prioritate decat stilurile tale! */\n@layer components {\n  .card { padding: 1.5rem; }  /* Suprascrie Bootstrap.card */\n}\n```\n\nLayer-uri nested:\n```css\n@layer framework {\n  @layer base {\n    .btn { color: white; }\n  }\n  @layer theme {\n    .btn { background: blue; }\n  }\n}\n/* Referinta: framework.base, framework.theme */\n\n/* Override din exterior: */\n@layer framework.theme {\n  .btn { background: #6366f1; }\n}\n```\n\nStiluri unlayered (fara @layer) au intotdeauna cea mai mare prioritate — suprascrieaza orice layer."
